{"type":"route","meta":{"status":200,"headers":{"content-type":"text/plain;charset=UTF-8","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/llms.txt/layout,_N_T_/llms.txt/route,_N_T_/llms.txt"}},"body":"# Docs\n\n- [Welcome to NxCut](/docs): Everything you need to run your salon — bookings, payments, staff, and more\n- [Dashboard](/docs/dashboard): A real-time overview of your salon's performance — revenue, appointments, and top staff\n- [Calendar & Bookings](/docs/calendar): Book, view, and manage all your salon appointments in one place\n- [Checkout](/docs/checkout): Collect payment, print receipts, and manage completed sales\n- [Sales Hub](/docs/sales): View, filter, and export your full sales history — appointments, payments, memberships, vouchers, products, and tips\n- [Catalog & Inventory](/docs/catalog): Set up your services, products, memberships, vouchers, and manage stock\n- [Clients](/docs/clients): Manage your client database — add, search, and view full client profiles\n- [Team Management](/docs/team): Add staff, set their schedules, and control what they can access\n- [Commission](/docs/commission): Set up commission rules for your staff and generate detailed salary slips\n- [Reporting & Analytics](/docs/reporting): Access all your salon reports — sales, finance, and team performance\n- [Settings](/docs/settings): Configure your branches, business hours, payment methods, and permissions\n- [Website & Booking Module](/docs/website): Manage your public booking Module and salon website profile"}